# Sentra Emoji Stickers Configuration
# 
# 表情包配置文件 - 映射文件名到含义描述
# 格式: FILENAME=Description
#
# 注意:
# 1. 文件名必须是 emoji-stickers/emoji 目录下实际存在的图片文件
# 2. 支持格式: .png, .jpg, .jpeg, .gif, .webp
# 3. 描述应该简洁明确，说明表情包的含义和使用场景
# 4. AI 会根据描述选择合适的表情包
# 5. 此配置文件独立于项目根目录的 .env，不会冲突
#
# 使用方法:
# 1. 复制此文件为 .env (去掉 .example 后缀)
# 2. 将表情包图片放入 emoji-stickers/emoji 子目录
# 3. 配置文件名和对应含义（只填文件名，不需要路径）
# 4. 重启服务生效
#
# ============================================

# 示例配置 (实际使用时替换为你的表情包)

# 可爱/卖萌类
cute_cat.png=A cute cat with big eyes, expressing adorable/innocent feelings
thinking_cat.png=A cat in thinking pose, use when pondering or considering something
sleeping_cat.png=A cat sleeping peacefully, use when tired or going to sleep
happy_dog.png=A happy dog wagging tail, expressing joy and excitement

# 表情反应类
thumbs_up.png=Thumbs up gesture, expressing approval or agreement
clap.png=Clapping hands, expressing appreciation or celebration
facepalm.png=Facepalm gesture, expressing embarrassment or disbelief
confused.png=Confused expression, use when uncertain or puzzled

# 情绪表达类
love_heart.png=Heart emoji, expressing love or strong liking
sad_face.png=Sad expression, use when empathizing with disappointment
surprised.png=Surprised face, use when shocked or amazed
laughing.png=Laughing face, use when something is funny

# 工作/学习类
studying.png=Character studying hard, use in learning contexts
working.png=Character working at computer, use in work-related contexts
celebrating.png=Celebrating with confetti, use when achieving success
tired.png=Exhausted character, use when overwhelmed or exhausted

# 动作/状态类
waving.png=Waving hand, use for greetings or goodbyes
nodding.png=Nodding in agreement, use when confirming or agreeing
shrugging.png=Shrugging shoulders, expressing uncertainty or "I don't know"
pointing.png=Pointing finger, use when highlighting something important

# 季节/节日类
snowman.png=Cute snowman, use in winter or holiday contexts
fireworks.png=Fireworks display, use for celebrations or special occasions
moon.png=Moon and stars, use in evening/night contexts
sun.png=Bright sun, use in cheerful/energetic contexts

# 食物相关类
coffee.png=Coffee cup, use when discussing caffeine or morning routines
cake.png=Birthday cake, use for celebrations or dessert discussions
pizza.png=Pizza slice, use in casual food discussions

# 其他实用类
check_mark.png=Green check mark, confirming completion or correctness
question_mark.png=Question mark, use when asking or clarifying
light_bulb.png=Light bulb, representing ideas or inspiration
sparkles.png=Sparkles/stars, adding emphasis or excitement

